{"data":[{"name":"101:1","price":"1. Het bonkende (het geluid van de dag des oordeels dat de harten angst geeft).","arabic":"ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6158,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"101:2","price":"2. Wat is het uur dat geslagen is?","arabic":"مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6159,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"101:3","price":"3. En wat laat jullie weten wat het uur dat geslagen is?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلۡقَارِعَةُ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6160,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"101:4","price":"4. Dat is de dag waarop de mensheid lijkt op verspreide motten.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَكُونُ ٱلنَّاسُ كَٱلۡفَرَاشِ ٱلۡمَبۡثُوثِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6161,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"101:5","price":"5. En de bergen zullen lijken op gekaarde wol.","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ ٱلۡمَنفُوشِ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6162,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"101:6","price":"6. Voor degenen wiens weegschaal zwaar is (aan Tawbah en goede daden).","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن ثَقُلَتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6163,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"101:7","price":"7. Hij zal een plezierig leven leiden.","arabic":"فَهُوَ فِي عِيشَةٖ رَّاضِيَةٖ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6164,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"101:8","price":"8. Maar voor degene wiens weegschaal licht is (zwaar in zijn eigen lusten volgen, licht in de profeet Mohammed vrede zij met hem volgen).","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَفَّتۡ مَوَٰزِينُهُۥ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6165,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"101:9","price":"9. Zijn toevlucht is de hel.","arabic":"فَأُمُّهُۥ هَاوِيَةٞ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6166,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"101:10","price":"10. En wat laat jullie weten wat dat is?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا هِيَهۡ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6167,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"101:11","price":"11. Dat is een heet laaiend vuur!","arabic":"نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ","category":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah"],"ayahNumber":6168,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"}],"chapter":["101 (Al-Qari'ah)","Al-Qari'ah","Surah Al-Qari'ah","Chapter Al-Qari'ah","Qari'ah","Surah Qari'ah","Chapter Qari'ah","Al Qari'ah","Surah Al Qari'ah","Chapter Al Qari'ah","Surah 101","Chapter 101","The Calamity","القارعة"]}